  "details": "The gnutls packages provide the GNU Transport Layer Security (GnuTLS) library, which implements cryptographic algorithms and protocols such as SSL, TLS, and DTLS.  \n\nSecurity Fix(es):  \n\n  * gnutls: GnuTLS Impacted by Inefficient DER Decoding in libtasn1 Leading to Remote DoS (CVE-2024-12243)\n\n\nFor more details about the security issue(s), including the impact, a CVSS score, acknowledgments, and other related information, refer to the CVE page(s) listed in the References section.\n",
